                        <h2 class="page-header__title">About Us</h2>
                        <div class="page-header__intro">Vickies Foundation is a non-governmental organisation which is
                            focused on the education and career development needs of Nigerian children, students and
                            youths. We recognise that education is the remedy for all kinds of social ills and that the
                            foundation of a good education is the means to pass on knowledge communicated through the
                            written medium of books.</div>
