            <div class="layout layout--margin_column bg-standard">
                <div class="layout__container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="layout__column-with-margin col-12 col-sm-6 offset-sm-1">
                            <div class="text-module">
                                <p>Books help give information concerning particular disciplines and therefore help in
                                    different kinds of research and reference.
                                    Books also help in recording important information that cannot or should not be
                                    forgotten for purposes of future reference.
                                    They are used as teaching materials in schools and other learning institutions as
                                    they record the curriculum that is used by teachers to deliver teaching to learners.
                                </p>
                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p>Young people quite rightly believe that education is vital to prosper in life and
                                    further one’s career potential. The hunger for knowledge of many students motivates
                                    them to attend school at all cost. The sad truth, however, is that often times,
                                    their parents cannot afford the books needed for their academic development and
                                    schools also often lack the necessary resources to provide these essential learning
                                    materials.
                                    Furthermore, many schools do not even have library facilities and as a result
                                    students and young people are not able to reach their potential in life. Books
                                    really are essential and fulfil a variety of needs from academic through to
                                    entertainment and relaxation. </p>

                            </div>
                            <div class="read_more-module read-more">
                                <button class="button read-more__button"><i class="icon plus"></i>Read More</button>
                                <div class="read-more__text">
                                    <!-- <h4>Languages</h4> -->
                                    <p>Vickies Foundation has been established in order to tackle the issue of failing
                                        education due to lack of access to books and learning materials. The Foundation
                                        sources and then donates books to these schools and educational institutions,
                                        enabling them to meet the primary needs of students.</p>
                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>


                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="layout__margin-column col-12 col-sm-3 offset-sm-1" id="mission">
                            <div class="quote-module quote">
                                <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                                <p>To support children, students and youths, enabling them to achieve their academic
                                    dreams and reach their full career potential.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
